readable.content: A dog with a Frisbee jumps over a man A large crowd of people are sitting watching a dog jump high up to catch a Frisbee with a man standing under the dog looking up at it . A man ducks down as a dog flies over his head to fetch a Frisbee . A white dog in a blue leaps over a man in a blue outfit with yellow stars in order to catch a Frisbee whilst people stand by and watch . Man and jumping dog perform Frisbee act for crowd at outdoor event .
